Class TGRouteRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.route.TGRouteRepository

  • @Beta
public class TGRouteRepository
extends java.lang.Object
    For use with transferring TGRoutes between contexts. There is a max internal size so do NOT use this class for more than just transferring routes.
